  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FANTATALE Grand Opening - 11/12!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If this game matches your style, don’t forget to add it to your WHISHLIST!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep following us for the latest news and updates. You won’t want to miss what’s coming next!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight, Lv up, Decorate! The moment when every fantasy becomes reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, your own special adventure begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/3cae1ccdeecd166707bfff13adbfd031.poster.avif?t=1766456317\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/3cae1ccdeecd166707bfff13adbfd031.webm?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/3cae1ccdeecd166707bfff13adbfd031.mp4?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Lv up to strengthen your CHARACTER]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face ever-changing boss patterns and dynamic combat situations on every floor!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn the tide with weapon swaps, and claim thrilling victories through strategy and teamwork.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the rush of battle and step onto a stage of endless challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/f376dfe4d0367969d8be4815dff8aa03.poster.avif?t=1766456317\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/f376dfe4d0367969d8be4815dff8aa03.webm?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/f376dfe4d0367969d8be4815dff8aa03.mp4?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Break Limits Through Growth]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow continuously through guilds, alliances, and world events, and pursue new goals within endless content!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your own economy through the item marketplace and experience limitless growth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On the path of endless adventure, the true joy of MMORPG awaits.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/877274037669ea819744d6de995cf6b3.poster.avif?t=1766456317\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/877274037669ea819744d6de995cf6b3.webm?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/877274037669ea819744d6de995cf6b3.mp4?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>[Enjoy a Fantasy Life Through Customization]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete your unique style with humorous costumes and charming accessories!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate your own home with the housing system and create a world full of laughter and joy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is more than just combat. It’s a space where your second life breathes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/a1778618520bf63038fb29ff717fc345.poster.avif?t=1766456317\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/a1778618520bf63038fb29ff717fc345.webm?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/a1778618520bf63038fb29ff717fc345.mp4?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/b0b07659fb198e556481e871bdd182f4.poster.avif?t=1766456317\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/b0b07659fb198e556481e871bdd182f4.webm?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/b0b07659fb198e556481e871bdd182f4.mp4?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight! Lv up! Decorate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the thrill of battle, the joy of growth, to the fun of customization — all your fantasies come true in one game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ultimate casual MMORPG – FANTATALE. Your story begins now.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FANTATALE Grand Opening - 11/12!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If this game matches your style, don’t forget to add it to your WHISHLIST!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep following us for the latest news and updates. You won’t want to miss what’s coming next!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight, Lv up, Decorate! The moment when every fantasy becomes reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, your own special adventure begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/3cae1ccdeecd166707bfff13adbfd031.poster.avif?t=1766456317\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/3cae1ccdeecd166707bfff13adbfd031.webm?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/3cae1ccdeecd166707bfff13adbfd031.mp4?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Lv up to strengthen your CHARACTER]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face ever-changing boss patterns and dynamic combat situations on every floor!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn the tide with weapon swaps, and claim thrilling victories through strategy and teamwork.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the rush of battle and step onto a stage of endless challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/f376dfe4d0367969d8be4815dff8aa03.poster.avif?t=1766456317\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/f376dfe4d0367969d8be4815dff8aa03.webm?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/f376dfe4d0367969d8be4815dff8aa03.mp4?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Break Limits Through Growth]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow continuously through guilds, alliances, and world events, and pursue new goals within endless content!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your own economy through the item marketplace and experience limitless growth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On the path of endless adventure, the true joy of MMORPG awaits.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/877274037669ea819744d6de995cf6b3.poster.avif?t=1766456317\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/877274037669ea819744d6de995cf6b3.webm?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/877274037669ea819744d6de995cf6b3.mp4?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>[Enjoy a Fantasy Life Through Customization]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete your unique style with humorous costumes and charming accessories!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate your own home with the housing system and create a world full of laughter and joy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is more than just combat. It’s a space where your second life breathes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/a1778618520bf63038fb29ff717fc345.poster.avif?t=1766456317\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/a1778618520bf63038fb29ff717fc345.webm?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/a1778618520bf63038fb29ff717fc345.mp4?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/b0b07659fb198e556481e871bdd182f4.poster.avif?t=1766456317\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/b0b07659fb198e556481e871bdd182f4.webm?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301040/extras/b0b07659fb198e556481e871bdd182f4.mp4?t=1766456317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight! Lv up! Decorate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the thrill of battle, the joy of growth, to the fun of customization — all your fantasies come true in one game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ultimate casual MMORPG – FANTATALE. Your story begins now.</p>",
